      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions documented with sufficient fidelity to support comparison with simulation boundary conditions.",
      "rationale": "FDA pump experimental data collected at 2500 RPM, flow rates 2.5–7.5 L/min, using bovine blood at 37°C. Test conditions recorded and traceable to published FDA dataset. Boundary condition mapping documented."
