      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric defined; simulation-to-experiment agreement within acceptable band for hemolysis index.",
      "rationale": "Normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared across five operating points. Mean absolute relative error 8.4%, within the 15% acceptance band defined for MRL 2. Validation metric formally computed."
